 "html": "<p>Soms kruis n gereg jou pad wat jou wereld verander.  Die piesangroomys is een van die lekkerste nageregte wat ek in my lewe geeet het.  Dis ongelooflik! Dis sag en romerig!<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-0291.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1358\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 029\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-0291-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>\n<p>BENODIG:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>6 piesangs<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-001.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1348\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 001\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-001-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>125 ml grondboontjiebotter<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-023.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1352\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 023\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-023-768x1024.jpg\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>NOU:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Sny die piesangs in dun ringetjies. <a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-008.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1349\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 008\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-008-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Plaas dit op n bakplaat en bedek met kleefplastiek.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-018.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1350\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 018\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-018-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Vries dit.</li>\n<li>Sit dit in jou voedselverwerker en kap fyn.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-019.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1351\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 019\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-019-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n<li>Meng die grondboontjiebotter by.<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-024.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1353\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 024\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-024-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Dis die lekkerste lekker in LekkerLand!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!<a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-027.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-large wp-image-1354\" alt=\"piesangroomys blog 027\" src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/piesangroomys-blog-027-1024x768.jpg\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\"></a></p>",
